# File Naming & Import Standards

## File Naming

- Use kebab-case for all files and directories
- Use PascalCase for component files
- Use descriptive names that indicate purpose

## Import Paths

- Use `@/*` for src directory imports
- Use `@mocks/*` for test mock imports
- Use `@testUtils` for test utility imports
- Use `@hamlet/*` for Hamlet API imports

## Import Organization

- Use simple-import-sort plugin rules
- Group imports: external libraries, internal modules, relative imports
- Use absolute imports with `@/*` alias for src directory
- Use `@mocks/*` for test mocks, `@testUtils` for test utilities
